com.algorand.algosdk.transaction

Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.algorand.algosdk.transaction.Transaction

  • public class Transaction
extends Object
    A raw serializable transaction class, used to generate transactions to broadcast to the network. This is distinct from algod.model.Transaction, which is only returned for GET requests to algod.

      • Transaction

        public Transaction(Address sender,
                   BigInteger fee,
                   BigInteger firstValid,
                   BigInteger lastValid,
                   byte[] note,
                   ParticipationPublicKey votePK,
                   VRFPublicKey vrfPK)
        Create a key registration transaction. No field can be null except the note field.
        Parameters:
        sender - source address
        fee - transaction fee
        firstValid - first valid round
        lastValid - last valid round
        note - optional notes field (can be null)
        votePK - the new participation key to register
        vrfPK - the sortition key to register
